STORM OVER LONDON
=================

This is an interactive fiction story written in [Hugo](http://www.generalcoffee.com/hugo/gethugo.html).

The compiled story file can be downloaded from http://nitku.net/if/storm/storm.hex. You need an interpreter to play (see e.g. http://www.sidneymerk.com/hugofree.shtml).

Compiling
---------

You'll need the [Hugo compiler](http://www.generalcoffee.com/hugo/gethugo.html).

    hc @source=src @lib=lib src/storm
